dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents the airport locations of the world at 1:250,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. World Airports provides a base map layer for the airport locations of the world. DeLorme Publishing Company and ESRI. (2014). World Airports, 2013. ESRI. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/zy985vy4585
